www.nme.com/artists/electric-light-orchestra">Elo</a>将于今年夏天在海德公园（Hyde Park）举行告别表演，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeff-lynnes-elo-announces-farewell-show-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2025-buy-tickets-3804580">将于7月13日星期日扮演Great Oak舞台</a>。美国乡村明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zach-bryan">扎克·布莱恩（Zach Bryan）</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zach-bryan-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3806223">被宣布为头条新闻</a>，并定于6月28日至29日进入Great Oak舞台， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zach-bryan-adds-extra-london-show-at-bst-hyde-park-2025-due-to-phenomenal-demand-buy-tickets-3808323">由于“惊人的需求”，</a>后者是额外的演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-her-biggest-ever-uk-show-at-bst-hyde-park-2025-3811479">Olivia Rodrigo</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noah-kahan-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3809226">Noah Kahan</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3819535">Sabrina Carpenter</a>也将分别于6月27日，7月4日和7月5日在Hyde Park演出。</p><p>在其他休·杰克曼（Hugh Jackman）新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-reynolds">瑞安·雷诺兹（Ryan Reynolds）</a>最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/watch-ryan-reynolds-surprise-hugh-jackman-at-opening-night-of-his-new-york-concert-series-3832026">在纽约无线电城音乐厅举行的演出的开幕之夜使杰克曼感到惊讶</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hugh-jackman-cancels-huge-london-bst-hyde-park-2025-show-3834159">休·杰克曼（Hugh Jackman）帖子“深感失望”，以取消伦敦BST Hyde Park 2025 Show的巨大表演，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
