ed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/120-people-are-working-on-new-lawsuits-against-diddy-for-sexual-abuse-including-25-minors-3798823">over 120 people had come forward with new allegations – including 25 minors</a> .</p><p> More recently, he was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-accused-of-groping-making-the-band-contestant-and-threatening-to-eat-bandmates-flesh-3829865">accused of threatening to eat the flesh of one of the contestants on his 2000s music competition show</a> <em>Making The Band.</em> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Diddy: The Making of a Bad Boy |官方预告片| Peacock Original" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dv0A5zqv0SE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> New documentary <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/how-to-watch-the-diddy-documentary-making-of-a-bad-boy-in-the-uk-3828913"><em>The Making of a Bad Boy</em> was released last month</a> on <em>Peacock,</em> and explores Diddy&#39;s early life and career, featuring interviews with people close to the rap mogul. In the film, former Bad Boy Records signee Sara Rivers accuses Combs of threatening her and her bandmates during her time on the show between 2002 and 2004.</p><p> “When he got angry with one of my band members, he said, &#39;You make me so mad I want to eat your flesh,&#39;” Rivers said. “And then he said to another one of my band members, he said, &#39;You&#39;re rolling your eyes, I could go get a crackhead and pay them $20 to smack the shit out of you.&#39;谁说？ That&#39;s crazy.”</p><p> The 47-year-old also accused Diddy of groping her during filming: “He touched me in a place that he shouldn&#39;t have.那是不合适的。 I felt intimidated, I felt like, &#39;Oh my god, what the heck just happened just now?&#39;” </p><figure id="attachment_3828927" 