ener"><em>Variety</em></a> ): “It is disappointing to see <em>NBC</em> and Peacock rolling in the same mud as unethical tabloid reporters. By providing a platform for proven liars and opportunists to make false criminal accusations, the documentary is irresponsible journalism of the worst kind.” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-drops-bail-appeal-will-remain-in-jail-until-may-trial-3822165"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-requests-access-to-laptop-in-prison-to-assist-in-his-defence-3820023"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> <b>For more help, advice or more information regarding sexual harassment, assault and rape in the UK, visit the</b> <a href="http://rapecrisis.org.uk/index.php"><b>Rape Crisis charity website</b></a> <b>. In the US, visit</b> <a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php"><b>RAINN.</b></a></p></div></div></div></div><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-reportedly-hospitalised-while-awaiting-trial-for-sex-trafficking-charges-3834084">Diddy reportedly hospitalised while awaiting trial for sex trafficking charges</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
